How It Works
Privacy first
Chats are not visible to other Yupp users by default, but users can choose to make their interactions public. User feedback contributes to our leaderboard in a privacy-preserving manner.
Real users, real insight
More than simple thumbs-up-thumbs-down. Rich profiles coupled with advanced prompt analytics give us unparalleled ability to slice-and-dice preference data.
Robust and trustworthy data
Evals that are representative, realistic, and gaming-resistant. Our evaluation platform is neutral, transparent, and built on rigorous scientific principles.
